---
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<main class="relative mx-auto px-8 max-w-5xl py-12 md:px-12">
  <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-negroni-500 text-center mb-6">
      Order Now - Get Your Brownies Delivered!
    </h1>

    <div class="text-lg text-gray-800 leading-relaxed space-y-6">
      <p>
        <strong>Craving something sweet yet healthy?</strong> Order our delicious Baby Brownies and get them delivered straight to your door! 
        Whether it's a special occasion, a surprise for someone, or just a treat for yourself - we make it easy.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-negroni-500">How to Order?</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li> <strong>Send us a WhatsApp message</strong> with your name and delivery address.</li>
        <li> <strong>Choose your brownies</strong>  Hearth Brownie, Hearth Buzzy Brownie, 9-Piece Set, or 2-Piece Set.</li>
        <li> <strong>We confirm your order</strong> and send you payment details.</li>
        <li> <strong>Your brownies are delivered fresh</strong> right to your doorstep!</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-negroni-500">Contact Us on WhatsApp</h2>
      <p>
        Simply send us your address and order details on WhatsApp, and we will handle the rest! 
        Click the button below to start your order. 
      </p>

      <p class="text-center mt-6">
        <a href="https://wa.me/12406103450" class="bg-negroni-500 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-negroni-600 transition">
          Order via WhatsApp
        </a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>
